text: Victor Randiki Ochieng (born 20 March 1991) is a Kenyan former footballer who played as a striker. ==Career== Born in Nairobi, Ochieng played club football for KCB, Chemelil Sugar, A.F.C. Leopards, SoNy Sugar, Posta Rangers and Western Stima.
